caption:
🚀 Get ready for GDSC Tech Nexus!*🚀

An incredible 2-day event by GDSC DJSCE to elevate your technical skills 🤩
📅 Day 1: ML Workshop- _Trek through TensorFlow_
🔍 Dive into the world of Machine Learning with hands-on TensorFlow model creation! Learn the ins and outs of building powerful ML models!

📅 Day 2: App Dev Workshop: _Flutter Forward_
📱 Explore the fusion of ML and app development! Discover how to seamlessly integrate Machine Learning into your Flutter apps and unlock endless possibilities.

🎓 Plus, receive a certificate for attending both days and expanding your skills!

📅 Date: 29th and 30th April
🕑 Time: 6:00 PM onwards
🏢 Venue: Online

Register now from link in BIO!

For any queries, contact us at:
Nishtha Chitalia : 9619268132
Aryan Gupta : 9653170445

Mark your calendars and join us for an unforgettable journey into the realms of tech innovation! 🌐✨

24 hours of non-stop coding, ideating, and building, and our hackers have done it at HackNiche 2.0! 🏆👨‍💻👩‍💻 We are excited to announce the winners of our 24-hour hackathon:

1st Place: All Stackers🥇
2nd Place: ITerative Bytes 🥈
3rd Place: DODS 🥉

Your passion and perseverance have paid off, and we're in awe of the innovative solutions you've created at #HackNiche2.0. You've proven that with determination and collaboration, anything is possible! 💪💻 Congrats to all the winners, and we can't wait to see what you'll do next! 🎉🚀 #HackathonWinners #InnovativeSolutions #TechInnovators
